The Green Glowstone Tavern is located near one end of the Crimson Corridor on Coruscant. Lorn Pavan and I-5YQ often visited it, despite it officially not allowing droids.

The Tusken Oasis is a nightclub owned by Yanth the Hutt. It is located in Coruscant's Crimson Corridor. Its amusements include a bar, a Bith quartet, dejarik boards, sabacc tables, and dancing girls. It is well kept and its decoration include colored lights and statuettes of various mythological beasts.
